OL,3,CMan jailed for biting man's ear off in
OL,4,C'sickening' attack
OL,6,FA man has been jailed after biting a
OL,7,Fman's ear off in an horrific attack.
OL,8,FOn 26 October 2023, Lancashire Police
OL,9,Fwere called to reports of an assault
OL,10,Fat a flat on Bolton Rd, Darwen.
OL,12,FWhen they got there they found a man
OL,13,Fin his 50s unresponsive, with a number
OL,14,Fof injuries including one of his ears
OL,15,Fbeing bitten off.
