OL,6,FHe was rushed to hospital and such was
OL,7,Fthe severity of his injuries, which
OL,8,Fincluded a collapsed lung and a bleed
OL,9,Fon the brain, that it was initially
OL,10,Ffeared he may die, but he survived
OL,11,Fafter a number of operations.
OL,13,FThe man responsible for the attack,
OL,14,FSteven Paterson, was arrested at the
OL,15,Fscene and later charged.
