OL,3,CMan jailed for biting man's ear off in
OL,4,C'sickening' attack
OL,6,FPaterson, 35, of Cavendish Street,
OL,7,FDarwen, pleaded guilty to Section 18
OL,8,Fwounding at Preston Crown Court, and
OL,9,Fon Monday 29 April, was jailed for
OL,10,Fnine years and five months with an
OL,11,Fextended licence of five years.
OL,13,FTony Roberts, of Blackburn CID, said:
OL,14,F"This was a sickening and callous
OL,15,Fattack which has left Paterson's
OL,16,Fvictim with life-threatening injuries.
OL,18,F"Nothing can justify the ferocious
OL,19,Fviolence used in the attack, which
OL,20,Fincluded the victim losing part of his
OL,21,Fears.
